These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, crime, family, sports, thriller, mystery, time-travel
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: trance, d&b, gospel, folk, punk, indie, techno
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: biathlon, soccer, ice-hockey, skiing, sailing, cricket, handball
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is between the fan of d&b and the fan of trance##2
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's sport is handball##1
 7. the fan of folk is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person watching thriller movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is the fan of gospel##1
11. the fan of indie is the person watching sports movies##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the person who's sport is biathlon is the fan of punk##1
14. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is handball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | zombie     | mystery | crime | sports | time-travel  | family  |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | folk        | d&b  | techno     | indie   | gospel       | punk   |
| Sport         | soccer   | handball | skiing    | ice-hockey  | sailing | cricket | biathlon |

