.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, argentine, australian, polish, dutch, spanish, french
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skiing, climbing, cycling, baseball, biathlon, basketball, water-polo
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, van, airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, boat, quad-bike
 1. the argentine is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is the french##1
 6. the turkish is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the turkish is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the dutch##1
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the australian is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the dutch is on the right of the turkish##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is the argentine##1
13. the polish is on the left of the turkish##1
14. the polish is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
15. the argentine is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | spanish | french      | polish     | turkish  | dutch | australian | argentine |
| Sport         | climbing  | skiing | basketball | cycling | water-polo | baseball   | biathlon  |
| Transport     | airplane   | boat     | quad-bike        | jet-ski  | motorbike   | van       | helicopter      |

