 3. the person driving the train is on the right of the electrician##1
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person drinking cola##1
 5. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the bike and the pilot##2
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the pilot##1
 9. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
10. the police-officer is on the right of the librarian##1
11. the person driving the motorbike is the nurse##1
12. the police-officer is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the doctor##1
14. the person driving the bike is the person drinking lemonade##1
15. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

