The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, journalist, pilot, security-guard, architect, chef
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: techno, jazz, rock, pop, disco, soul, indie
7 different pets are kept: dog, fish, pony, horse, goat, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the journalist##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is between the fan of disco and the fan of rock##2
 3. the fan of techno is the owner of the fish##1
 4. the fan of indie is on the left of the architect##1
 5. the fan of techno is the accountant##1
 6. the journalist is in the middle##1
 7. the security-guard is the fan of soul##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the fan of techno is the owner of the fish##1
10. the chef is the owner of the goat##1
11. the accountant is on the right of the pilot##1
12. the fan of indie is on the left of the architect##1
13. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
14. the fan of jazz is on the left of the accountant##1
15. the chef is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | dressmaker | architect | security-guard | journalist  | chef   | pilot | accountant      |
| Music-Genre   | indie | rock        | soul    | disco     | pop     | jazz   | techno        |
| Pet           | dog   | pony       | goldfish    | horse | goat | rabbit   | fish |

