.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-17::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, rock-climbing, singing, skydiving, card-games, puzzles, writing
7 different pets are kept: bird, fish, mouse, hamster, chinchilla, snake, cat
The people use 7 different means of transport: train, subway, bus, car, van, tram, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
 2. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the fish##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 9. the owner of the bird is the person driving the van##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is the owner of the chinchilla##1
13. the person driving the car is the owner of the snake##1
14. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person driving the train##1
15. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |    5    |   6    |   7    |
