 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
