The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skateboarding, baseball, cricket, biathlon, surfing, lacrosse, cycling
 1. the scientist is on the left of the engineer##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 5. the coach is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 6. the engineer is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the person watching romance movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
11. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the doctor##1
12. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the musician and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
13. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
15. the librarian is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

