.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade, milk, water, tea, juice
The people have 7 different hobbies: video-games, puzzles, collecting, reading, baking, camping, woodworking
7 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, goat, bird, dog, horse, hamster
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the horse is the person drinking milk##1
 7. the owner of the goat is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the owner of the bird is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the owner of the goat##2
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
14. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the owner of the hamster and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
15. the owner of the hamster is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | juice  | tea   | water   | milk        | lemonade     | hot-chocolate | soy-milk       |
| Hobby      | video-games | puzzles | woodworking | reading | collecting  | baking   | camping |
| Pet        | hamster   | hedgehog     | mouse     | horse      | dog | bird    | goat      |

 